## 9. SUMMARY

B152 is the **hub** around which all Greatwood 1–20 work orbits.

- It does **not** replace B151 (loot) or the Hunts/Contracts files.
- It makes them **coherent**, so:
  - You can build Greatwood in phases.
  - You can check that it behaves as intended.
  - You can see, at a glance, what’s missing.

If B151 is “what drops where and why,”  
B152 is “how all of that fits together so Greatwood actually feels like a place.”

